Release Build
-------------

Document version
  Set new version in configure.in
  Set new windos version in src/defines.h
  Update ChangeLog
  Update NEWS
  Update AUTHORS
  Update THANKS 

Test it on Linux (optional)
  make distcheck

Test it on Solaris (optional)
  configure && make && make check 

Set version in configure.in and do
  git commit -m"new release" configure.in src/defines.h

Tag new release
  git tag <major>.<minor>.<maint>
  git push --tags

Build release
  ./release.sh HTT_RELEASE_<major>_<minor>_<maint>

Upload release
./upload.sh HTT_RELEASE_<major>_<minor>_<maint>

Set version in configure.in and src/defines.h to undef and do
  cvs -q ci -m"Release build"

Build Configure Script
----------------------

./buildconf.sh

